{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/qrcube/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"65a4a6ae-7639-5649-bc97-6e28870ad98b","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fa22a9fd530f1183689a3ee1d952c382/dbdff/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/fa22a9fd530f1183689a3ee1d952c382/dbdff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fa22a9fd530f1183689a3ee1d952c382/d1f95/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/fa22a9fd530f1183689a3ee1d952c382/dbdff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>QRCube is a trivial game that uses QR Codes to trigger the questions. It’s built using a custom template (50x50x50 mm) that you need to print and glue to form a cube.</p>\n<p>Each side has a QR Code with a different color and represents a team or a player. Each team has to throw the cube by turns and scan the code on top. After scanning, you get redirected to a URL with a random question for the team whose color corresponds to the code scanned.</p>\n<p>The app allows the players and teams to signup (to create their own QR code) and join the game and also keeps track of the correct/failed answers.</p>","fields":{"prefix":"2012"},"frontmatter":{"title":"QRCube game","categories":"wcrs open-source web installation prototype ux design","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/cbce3dd788d0cd0d06403bb7db39dcd5/47498/logo.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/qrcube/","source":"work"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}